snippet.title: Kura5: Bonds of the Undying - Version 0.2 Update
snippet.description:
Howdy howdy. It's been a while!

Kura5 has been updated to version 0.2, which is almost entirely different if you've played 0.1 at all. 

Remember to be mindful of what time you play! Picking up sunlight through Weather Sync might not only affect gameplay, but story as well...

Download it here!
https://chickenhat.itch.io/kura5-bonds-of-the-undying

Music by LiteralLapin
Bandcamp - https://literallapin.bandcamp.com
Soundcloud - https://soundcloud.com/literallapin

Follow us at...
twitter: https://twitter.com/boktai3d
tumblr: http://kura5.tumblr.com
discord: http://discord.gg/uJRmcyk
twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/catsfrommars
